# Glossary

Shared vocabulary for this project. Define a term once, here, and link to it from
rules, feature docs, and specs instead of redefining. Keep definitions to a
sentence or two; point to the code or feature doc for detail.

## Terms

### [Term]
<One-or-two-sentence definition. Note the canonical code location if one exists.>

### [Term]
<Definition.> See `.claude/features/[feature].md`.

### [Acronym] ([Expansion])
<What it means in this project's context — not the generic industry meaning if they differ.>

## Conventions

- Alphabetical within a section.
- If two terms are used interchangeably in conversation but mean different things
  in code, say so explicitly — that ambiguity is exactly what a glossary fixes.
